sentences: He played for various projects, being: xDISCIPLEx A.D., No Innocent Victim, Shockwave, and Jesus Wept.
He currently works for Facedown Records as a Graphic Designer.
Quiggle is married to Shannon Quiggle, (since 1999) a fellow employee of Facedown Records.
Dan Quiggle, xDISCIPLEx A.D.'s Vocalist, is Dave's brother.
Prayer for a Fallen Angel – guitar (1997)
